    <name>Halo 1 CE - SPV3</name>
    <summary></summary>
    <description>
        <p>SPV3 is the culmination of a vision that was started over 10 years ago, to revamp the 
        original  Halo campaign with features and ideas from later games, expanded fiction, and 
        cut content originally envisioned for Halo CE. With a strong emphasis of preserving the 
        addictive and tuned gameplay of the original, and a stellar Legendary difficulty, SPV3 
        focuses extensively on retaining that Halo CE feel.</p>
    </description>

